    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_4359581619" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4359581619" />
    <a title="Rambling Redhead" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/143417957-rambling-redhead"><img alt="Rambling Redhead" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1643978923p2/143417957.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4359581619?book_show_action=true">Nov 27, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rambling Redhead" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rambling Redhead" href="/user/show/143417957-rambling-redhead">Rambling Redhead</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/143417957-rambling-redhead?shelf=true-crime">true-crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/143417957-rambling-redhead?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/143417957-rambling-redhead?shelf=deadly-women">deadly-women</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4359581619" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17950257683775231929">Diane Downs, divorced mother of three, started an affair with a fellow employee. She dreamed of a life together. Small catch though, he doesn&apos;t want children, which sets the stage for a horrific scene. One night while driving home a &quot;bushy haired&quot; stranger shoots into her car killing one child, crippling another, and leaving the last barely alive. As the police race to find the culprit, they discover things are not as they seem. Did a mother commit the ultimate betrayal? Ann Rule, as usual, did </span>
  <span id="freeText17950257683775231929" style="display:none">Diane Downs, divorced mother of three, started an affair with a fellow employee. She dreamed of a life together. Small catch though, he doesn't want children, which sets the stage for a horrific scene. One night while driving home a "bushy haired" stranger shoots into her car killing one child, crippling another, and leaving the last barely alive. As the police race to find the culprit, they discover things are not as they seem. Did a mother commit the ultimate betrayal? Ann Rule, as usual, did a wonderful job.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17950257683775231929" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
