<div id="review_4257834316" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4257834316" />
    <a title="Derek Shouba" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/38040584-derek-shouba"><img alt="Derek Shouba" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1418864179p2/38040584.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4257834316?book_show_action=true">Sep 26, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Derek Shouba" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Derek Shouba" href="/user/show/38040584-derek-shouba">Derek Shouba</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38040584-derek-shouba?shelf=true-crime">true-crime</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4257834316" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12472470651229773491">Addictive genre true crime. Rule strives for accuracy and avoids gothic embellishment. I don’t know what is so compelling about true crime. I think it reminds us of minor tragedies we’ve survived. It must also make us more pleased with the joys of our quotidian lives. Perhaps it is a necessary reminder of mortality in a secular age. Perhaps it’s a pathology. Perhaps it signifies nothing.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

